# GitHub Linguist — files to NOT count as a language
# (They still appear in the repo, just excluded from language statistics.)

# External guides downloaded from The Buddy Forum (huge HTML scraped pages)
# are bundled for offline reference in output/Guides/, but they're not
# the project's own source code. Mark them as documentation so they
# don't skew the language stats.
output/Guides/*.html linguist-documentation
output/Guides/*.pdf  linguist-documentation
